export-entities.name: Sample/Sales/Sales Forecast Handling
export-entities.pql: ID 88 STATUS DRAFT CREATOR "0" ACCESS_POLICY ACCESS_CONTROL PBAC FOR TRUE ON ADMIN BY appuser.did = 0 DO allow PBAC FOR TRUE ON READ BY appuser.did = 0 DO allow PBAC FOR TRUE ON DEPLOY BY appuser.did = 0 DO allow PBAC FOR TRUE ON APPROVE BY appuser.did = 0 DO allow PBAC FOR TRUE ON WRITE BY appuser.did = 0 DO allow PBAC FOR TRUE ON DELETE BY appuser.did = 0 DO allow ALLOWED_ENTITIES POLICY "Sample/Sales/Sales Forecast Handling" DESCRIPTION "Prevents duplication of sales forecasting information to uncontrolled locations and prevents distribution of sales forecasting information via email or instant messaging." ATTRIBUTE USAGE FOR (TRUE AND (FALSE OR GROUP="RESOURCE/Controlled Sales Areas")) ON (TRUE AND (GROUP="ACTION/Duplicate" OR GROUP="ACTION/Distribute")) TO (TRUE AND NOT ((FALSE OR GROUP="RESOURCE/Controlled Sales Areas"))) BY ((TRUE AND TRUE) AND (TRUE AND TRUE) AND (TRUE AND TRUE)) DO deny ON deny DO log
